# Rust extension `.so` symlinks placed by `scripts/build_rust_extension.sh`
# into the `cutctx/` package dir for local development. The real binary
# lives in `crates/cutctx-py/python/cutctx/`; this is the dev overlay
# that lets `import cutctx._core` resolve when the source `cutctx/`
# package shadows the maturin overlay on sys.path.
/cutctx/_core.*.so
/cutctx/_core.so
*.whl
*.tar.gz

